{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99710-fa-di-he-tangguo","title":"法蒂和汤锅","description":"法蒂一向来都跑得很快，并且又一次地在她学校的运动日证明了这一点。 当她从学校回家时，她帮妈妈准备了欧克汤。 汤闻起来味道真美味，法蒂忍不住想喝！法蒂和汤锅是基于在加纳北部长大的女孩的真实冒险经验。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Eric Nii  Addy"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99710-fa-di-he-tangguo"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101361/size3/65a19ebf8ebc1992566927780b60359d.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101361/size6/65a19ebf8ebc1992566927780b60359d.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63777/size6/289117ef6d810ab950e1a88ca2daa33f.jpg","text":"法蒂是一个像风一样奔跑的小女孩，她喜欢笑，并且总是非常努力的完成她所被交代的事。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63778/size6/8edeb178bfde775b8fd728ad152d0bed.jpg","text":"今天是学校的运动日。\n法蒂踢足球，参加了三场比赛。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63779/size6/9353754053d800d6d510ea300ae07b2b.jpg","text":"放学后，她和她的好朋友哈瓦一起走回家。\n哈瓦说：“法蒂，你跑得好快！”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63780/size6/e1468b73641bd2814ac9fa60ab4cacea.jpg","text":"法蒂回到家，发现她的母亲在厨房里。\n她说：“妈妈，晚上好。”\n法蒂的母亲回答：“晚上好。 你好吗？”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63781/size6/a1ce1898f35195d7c68b0c55e379c9d0.jpg","text":"法蒂说：“我们今天在学校有运动日，而且我跑得很快。\n我很热，很累，很饿。”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63782/size6/912deb37b2347ee0143e64b6de1342d8.jpg","text":"妈妈笑着说：“亲爱的小法蒂，你出生时就腿快！\n我会煮欧克汤，晚餐很快就可以吃了。”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63783/size6/99b00d4f53311838fc4f1a2e1f550208.jpg","text":"妈妈把一些棕榈油放在一个大的烹饪锅里，放在火上。\n当油热起来时，她加入洋葱和大蒜，搅拌它们直到它们变软。\n然后她放入胡椒，西红柿，加入一些水和六块蒸牛肉。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63784/size6/c754806329788fc729f109c65e6f0162.jpg","text":"妈妈说，“法蒂，请帮助我搅匀汤。”\n法蒂说：“是的，妈妈。”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63785/size6/a1b28f7c7e57ca2a6116a13f34e7529a.jpg","text":"法蒂搅匀了一次汤。\n她说，“这汤味道好香。”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63787/size6/f861ded3f7db036bf6473752b97609d5.jpg","text":"法蒂搅匀了两次汤。\n她说，“这汤味道非常香。”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63788/size6/a1d2e1837b1d2fed9352e9a39b562d9c.jpg","text":"法蒂搅匀了三次汤。\n她说，“这汤闻起来非常，非常，香。”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63790/size6/13f2f1e8108b71f23b144e5b73ef6fa1.jpg","text":"然后，法蒂看着她的母亲。\n母亲没有在看法蒂。\n她正在切绿叶，准备把它放入汤。","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63791/size6/a682b94e641e5d5fa84a1b5342744e66.jpg","text":"法蒂从锅里拿了一块肉，把它吃了。\n法蒂说，“嗯......”","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63792/size6/e14410edca9a04ed55e48398b225a9a9.jpg","text":"法蒂再次看着她的母亲。\n母亲没有在看法蒂。\n她正在切鸡蛋，准备把它放入汤里。","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63793/size6/3da8cbb18e6d507f8ca948b582212def.jpg","text":"法蒂很快从锅里取出第二块肉，把它吃了。\n法蒂说：“嗯...... 嗯......”","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63794/size6/ce9ee4521c7a476a08490fc15d3057a6.jpg","text":"法蒂一再次看着她的母亲。\n母亲没有在看法蒂。\n她正在切欧克，准备把它放入汤里。","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63795/size6/5aa593424fe346acf743ed4021ba5ad9.jpg","text":"法蒂很快从锅里取出了第三块肉，也把它吃了！\n法蒂说：“嗯...... 嗯... 嗯......”","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63796/size6/a2016ddc7a950464c54ce6aefeb5288f.jpg","text":"不久，母亲拿着绿叶，鸡蛋和欧克来到了火堆。\n法蒂仍然拿着大木勺。","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63797/size6/544d4e7a98a6c8338576e296cb3ad0bf.jpg","text":"母亲微笑着说：“谢谢你帮助搅匀汤，法蒂。”\n法蒂不知道该说些什么。","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63798/size6/5108e2a8331c20f62d1a52b1ac0c7b44.jpg","text":"母亲把绿叶，鸡蛋和欧克放入汤中，从法蒂取了勺子。\n她开始搅匀汤。","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63799/size6/8bc621fceaaafff28fbe06243bcaede8.jpg","text":"母亲看进锅里。 她可以看到汤在烈火中冒泡。 母亲在锅里寻找那六块肉。\n“一......二......三......”母亲说。 母亲只看到了三块肉。\n母亲什么也没说。 法蒂什么也没说。","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63800/size6/f8ba24017bbe8695cb61fa47e5ad9b2f.jpg","text":"当母亲端上汤时，法蒂没有得到任何肉。\n法蒂说：“妈妈，对不起。 我不会再那样做了。”\n他从后就没有这样做了。\n那个故事就这么结束了。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":22,"words":60}}